<h1>Welcome to self-monitoring!</h1>
<p>The application provides users an opportunity to report behavior daily.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Sleep duration and sleep quality</li>
    <li>Time spent on sports and exercise</li>
    <li>Time spent studying</li>
    <li>Regularity and quality of eating</li>
    <li>Generic mood</li>
</ul>

<a href="http://localhost:7777/behavior/reporting"><strong>Click to report!</strong></a>
